The paper deals with image analysis and classification using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning models for geolocation is also a key aspect of the paper, which suggests that it could also be classified under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which could place it under information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper deals with photo albums and temporal coherence, which suggests that it could also be classified under multimedia (cs.MM).
